# Local Agent Overrides (Do Not Commit)

## Purpose
- Use this file for local, developer-specific instructions.
- Copy this file to `AGENTS.local.md` and edit only your local copy.
- `AGENTS.local.md` must stay untracked (see `.gitignore`).

## Local Downloader Values (Example)
- qBittorrent URL: `http://localhost:8080/`
- Transmission URL: `http://localhost:9091/`
- Transmission username: `<your-transmission-username>`
- Transmission password: `<your-transmission-password>`

## Safety
- Never copy real local values back into `AGENTS.md`, docs, tests, fixtures, or examples.
